elementValueMap.COBFailedText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseCOBChange%,'Yes') && %ImplementationCaseCOB%='NA',"Rule: Since the field “Are There Changes To The COB” = Yes, you must complete the “Indicate COB Record” field : ",'NA')
elementValueMap.COBSuccessText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseCOBChange%,'Yes') && %ImplementationCaseCOB%!='NA',"Rule: Since the field “Are There Changes To The COB” = Yes, you must complete the “Indicate COB Record” field : ",'NA')
elementValueMap.EligibilityFailedText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle'))&& EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseEligibilityChange%,'Yes') && %ImplementationCaseEligibility%='NA',"Rule: Since the field “Are There Changes To Eligibility” = Yes, you must complete the “Indicate Eligibility Record” field :  ",'NA')
elementValueMap.EligibilitySuccessText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseEligibilityChange%,'Yes') && %ImplementationCaseEligibility%!='NA',"Rule: Since the field “Are There Changes To Eligibility” = Yes, you must complete the “Indicate Eligibility Record” field : ",'NA')
elementValueMap.Implementercheck: =IF(EQUALS(%ProfileName%, null),'Y',IF(AND(CONTAINS(%AccountAnthemEntity%,'National Accounts'),OR(EQUALS(%ProfileName%, 'National Implementations'),EQUALS(%ProfileName%, 'National Implementations Dual'))),'Y', IF(AND(EQUALS(%AccountAnthemEntity%,'Local/Large Group'),OR(EQUALS(%ProfileName%, 'Local Implementations'),EQUALS(%ProfileName%, 'Local Implementations Dual'),EQUALS(%ProfileName%, 'Specialty'),EQUALS(%ProfileName%, 'Specialty Post Sales'))),'Y','N')))
